Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/IONIS-AI/ionis-apps
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: ionis-apps
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ionis-core (>= 3.0.0),
 ionis-apps-wspr (= ${binary:Version}),
 ionis-apps-solar (= ${binary:Version}),
 ionis-apps-contest (= ${binary:Version}),
 ionis-apps-pskr (= ${binary:Version})
Description: IONIS AI data pipeline applications (meta-package)
 Complete suite of WSPR, solar, contest, and PSK Reporter data pipeline
 tools for the IONIS Ionospheric Neural Inference System.

Package: ionis-apps-wspr
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IONIS AI WSPR data ingesters
 High-performance WSPR data ingesters for ClickHouse: wspr-turbo
 (streaming .gz), wspr-shredder (batch CSV), wspr-parquet-native,
 and wspr-download.

Package: ionis-apps-solar
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IONIS AI solar index pipeline
 Solar index download, ingest, and backfill tools for NOAA/SIDC/GFZ
 Potsdam data. Includes cron-ready solar-live-update (15-min) and
 solar-history-load (6-hour) scripts.

Package: ionis-apps-contest
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IONIS AI contest and RBN ingesters
 CQ contest Cabrillo log and Reverse Beacon Network data pipeline
 tools: contest-download, contest-ingest, rbn-download, rbn-ingest.

Package: ionis-apps-pskr
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IONIS AI PSK Reporter collector and ingester
 PSK Reporter MQTT real-time collector and ClickHouse ingester
 for live HF propagation monitoring.
